        "zh_tw": "能區分『我是學生』(一般介紹) 和『我才是學生』(指名主角) 的差別。",
        "en": "Tell the difference between 'I am a student' (intro) and 'I (am the one who) am a student' (focus)."
      },
      {
        "zh_tw": "能正確造出包含主語、受詞、動詞的簡單動作句。",
        "en": "Build basic sentence structures including subject, object, and verb."
      }
    ]
